name: Jazmín
description: '''Janeth Tatiana Mosquera Mera''' (born 10 May 1967), better known by her stage name '''Jazmín''', is an Ecuadorian singer of [[cumbia]] and [[tecnocumbia]]. Nicknamed '''La Tumbadora''' and '''La Reina de la Cumbia''', she is considered the rival of [[Sharon la Hechicera]]'s artistic performance since the late 1990s, but over the years they grew closer together as artistic partners.
